        "title": "三星电子将龙仁首座芯片厂投产提前至2029年，比原计划早1-2年",
        "uri": "https://wallstreetcn.com/articles/3776715"
      },
      "author": {
        "avatar": "https://wpimg-wscn.awtmt.com/3975af19-a3cf-40d4-908a-8f582b8fefcc",
        "display_name": "贺晨",
